### Solution:
```
def most_common_word(words):
    freq = {}
    for word in words:
        freq[word] = freq.get(word, 0) + 1
    max_freq = max(freq.values())
    max_word = None
    for word, freq in freq.items():
        if freq == max_freq:
            max_word = word
    return max_word
